data: A cool Python script that aim to get market data on Digimon cards!

Python script that utilizes the TCGPlayer API to store market data from Digmon cards with plans to use that data to create interactive graphs and attempt financial forecasting using time-series foracasting and regressio analysis.

May use Discord webhooks as a way to inform end-users about "great buys for the week" based on greatest positive or negative monetary differences.

Collborated with a Yu-Gi-Oh YouTuber who does card reviewing and deck-building to bring this to a wider audience once complete with some training data for the forecasting model.
